                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Identity, itinerary, and intent. Three boxes. Most people clear all three. Although — between us — the new database is missing rows this week. Walk-ins with faces the file room swears it has seen and the system swears it has not. Head office says that is normal. Head office says a lot of things are normal."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Checkpoint — the desk",
                    Label: "verify_desk"
                },
