                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "A page turns. The first voice reads the closing line flat, like weather. Reminder from head office — there was never a founder. Distribution ends. Destroy after reading. The memo sits in the dispatch tray, one arm-length from the flap."
                        }
                    ],
